metadata.name: MOUT Headquarters
metadata.description:
MOUT Headquarters is a place where the taste factory operates.

The minions are divided into two divisions, the office workers and the miners. The miners making sure the mines are free from dirt, while the office workers digitizing taste data from the central engine called the T.O.N.G.U.E

This is derived from a mouth diagram, which includes the tongue, teeth, uvula, etc. 

4961 x 7016 px
